&lt;h2 id="api-gateway-にデプロイ">
API Gateway にデプロイ
&lt;a href="#api-gateway-%e3%81%ab%e3%83%87%e3%83%97%e3%83%ad%e3%82%a4" class="h-anchor" aria-hidden="true">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ slss endpoint deploy
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Serverless: Deploying endpoints in &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;dev&amp;#34;&lt;/span> to the following regions: us-east-1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Serverless: Successfully deployed endpoints in &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;dev&amp;#34;&lt;/span> to the following regions:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Serverless: us-east-1 ------------------------
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>Serverless: GET - echo - https://xxxx.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/dev/echo
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>デプロイできました。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>$ curl -s &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;https://xxxx.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/dev/echo&amp;#34;&lt;/span> | jq .
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;message&amp;#34;&lt;/span>: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;Go Serverless! Your Lambda function executed successfully!&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>curl で実行すると、メッセージが返ってきました。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://mizu.dev/posts/2016/0324_api_gateway.jpg" alt="API Gatewayの設定値">&lt;/p>
